      h2 Emojis & Symbols
      p 🎉 🚀 ❤️ 🔥 💻 🌍 🌈 ⭐
      p Currency: €100 £50 ¥1000 ₹500
      p Math: ∑ ∏ √ ∞ ≈ ≠ ≤ ≥
